PREPARE PRESENCE ABSENCE DATA FOR PCA ANALYSIS

# 
library(dplyr)
library(tidyverse)
pres.abs.pca <- pres.abs %>%
                  select(Gene, starts_with("c.")) %>%
                  rename_at(vars(contains("c.")), ~gsub("c.", "", .x)) %>%
                  mutate_at(vars(-Gene), ~replace(., !is.na(.), 1)) %>%
                  mutate_at(vars(-Gene), list(~replace(., is.na(.), 0))) %>%
                  gather(var, value, -Gene) %>%
                  mutate(value = as.numeric(value)) %>%
                  spread(Gene, value) %>%
                  tibble::column_to_rownames(var = "var") %>%
                  as.matrix()
